							</a></figure></div></li>
					

	  

				
				
								
						
									<li><div class="feature-item image"><figure class="thumbnail"><a href="/ESA_Multimedia/Videos/2022/06/Asteroid_populations_in_Gaia_data_release_3" class="popup">
				<img class="image-bg" src="/var/esa/storage/images/esa_multimedia/videos/2022/06/asteroid_populations_in_gaia_data_release_3/24300854-1-eng-GB/Asteroid_populations_in_Gaia_data_release_3_pillars.jpg" alt="">
							</a></figure></div></li>
					

	  

				
				
								
						
									<li><div class="feature-item image"><figure class="thumbnail"><a href="/ESA_Multimedia/Videos/2022/06/Chemistry_of_asteroids_as_seen_by_Gaia" class="popup">
